      "type": "text-only",
      "settings": {
        "large_text": "",
        "small_text": "<p><strong>Welcome to the wonderful world of the revolutionary Gemini Build-A-Block™ Patchwork System. Whether you’re new to quilting and patchwork or a seasoned pro, Build-A-Block™ dies make it easy to design, cut and create a whole variety of quilt block designs in a range of sizes! Our time-saving dies feature a 1.5mm-thick cutting blade capable of cutting multiple layers of fabric with accuracy so you can focus on the fun parts of your quilting and patchwork projects.<\/strong><\/p>",
        "link_text": "Click here to purchase the Build-A-Block TM System",
        "link_url": "shopify:\/\/products\/gemini-build-a-block-patchwork-system",
        "left_align": false
      }
    },
    "ba624c2c-ac43-4ea7-ba10-b3007da3e9d4": {
      "type": "text-only",
      "settings": {
        "large_text": "Video Guides",
        "small_text": "<p>Our video guides provide easy-to-follow walkthroughs, top tips and expert advice from Lizzy Curtis. Videos feature an introduction to the Build-A-Block™ Patchwork System, how to construct a quilt block and inspirational project ideas.<\/p>",
        "link_text": "Click here to access the Video Guides",
        "link_url": "https:\/\/www.crafterscompanion.co.uk\/page\/build-a-block-videos\/",
        "left_align": false
      }
    },
